  "remarks": "\nSadrach Zeledón ROCHA is an involved person within the Global Human Rights (Sanctions) Regulations 2020 as ROCHA promoted, and incited serious human rights violations committed against protestors in the form of torture and cruel, inhuman and degrading treatment. Therefore, ROCHA has been involved in an activity that violated the right not to be subjected to torture or cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment or punishment.\n",
